io.github.noeppi_noeppi.libx.data.provider

Class AdvancementProviderBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.noeppi_noeppi.libx.data.provider.AdvancementProviderBase
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    net.minecraft.data.IDataProvider

    public abstract class AdvancementProviderBase
extends java.lang.Object
implements net.minecraft.data.IDataProvider
    base provider for custom advancements. If you want to have multiple advancement tabs, use multiple providers. Every provider has one root advancement all advancements with no explicit parent will be added to. You should configure your advancements with the root and advancement methods in setup().

      • root

        public AdvancementProviderBase.AdvancementFactory root(java.lang.String namespace,
                                                       java.lang.String id)
        Gets an AdvancementProviderBase.AdvancementFactory to customise the root advancement for this provider.
        Parameters:
        namespace - The namespace of the root advancement.
        id - The root advancement id. The real advancement id will be namespace:id/root All other advancements will then be put in namespace:id/advancement_id by default where id is the id given here.
